islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xa9Ekkf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxa9Ekkf.jpg&h=90c7ea8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無想像中咁痛，患處即時有白色嘅保護膜<br />\n即時舒緩到飛滋嘅痛楚<br />\n好見效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢隻野真係超有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b863f104a142f49a0d0ca19be3a2d4413f0ccc","tid":216761,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用之前索乾水，唔係聽日甩返出嚟你就知道乜嘢叫真正嘅地獄</blockquote><br />\n我有用紙巾印乾嘴唇先再搽。不過搽完之後好似仲腫咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98e4d2f2e7b57fe0057446ee9d952e8b0d1872f","tid":216761,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"之前用過，搽嗰一野有刺痛既感覺，之後就一啲都唔痛。其實咩原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81da23d005dbb0b617ef74073337efd750fbe562","tid":216761,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"Update 返先<br />\n<br />\n個傷口keep住唔痛，但仲係腫<br />\n<br />\n層白色保護膜仲喺到"},{"pid":"48ca26443b972b29f6603acb89a8c947d7d5d467","tid":216761,"uid":111670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:16:29.000Z","msg":"試過忍痛用鹽 諗住實無死喇<br />\n點知第2朝粒飛滋腫撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04571eb3c2fd077c41043f3b3c562ca7a00bc85","tid":216761,"uid":25676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過忍痛用鹽 諗住實無死喇<br />\n點知第2朝粒飛滋腫撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用後感係用鹽仲痛<br />\n<br />\n不過我噚晚係自己咬爆粒飛滋先再搽口健樂<br />\n<br />\n可以比咬爆飛滋嘅痛楚掩蓋咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d9a10a079ed4a857ed920460c89474507ab454","tid":216761,"uid":10111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:27:17.000Z","msg":"琴晚先用完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窮撚用完會用密實袋袋好擺入雪櫃，下次再用"},{"pid":"a8ec121d40996ce28bdfa06bde02504dddeb9f59","tid":216761,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前用過，搽嗰一野有刺痛既感覺，之後就一啲都唔痛。其實咩原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有化學乾燥劑<br />\n會令到痱滋表面細菌極速脫水死晒"},{"pid":"422298f16d6ecb534bc2efacb27299f0c7f24970","tid":216761,"uid":16783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"屌你 條利粒痱滋今日先謝<br />\n轉頭又咬到第2邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解我咁命苦 希望唔好發大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837f66b8d37c8f5a61e86d5768a53fac04ec6498","tid":216761,"uid":16783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:23:19.000Z","msg":"西瓜霜都唔錯<br />\n但有時個口太多菌就唔得"},{"pid":"190ccaea4468d9ef605a494763c93c91c6ebcb18","tid":216761,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:23:58.000Z","msg":"用完記得訓多啲，唔係個傷口又有機會再黎料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b5bde17c47fd0b96eb808df300924102130d1e","tid":216761,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:24:56.000Z","msg":"用必妥碘，好得，浪2日口已經好得7788<br />\n果陣個口有2粒飛滋查藥膏都唔好"},{"pid":"bcaa1e70f0951715113428aa3d51f978d5db5200","tid":216761,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"Update 返<br />\n<br />\n塊白色保護膜甩咗啦<br />\n<br />\n而家傷口好敏感，但唔痛<br />\n<br />\n諗緊好唔好搽多次"},{"pid":"f4fd1bce21cc8a897f27812e23d5db5d68f22271","tid":216761,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:47:16.000Z","msg":"喉嚨生點搞<br />\n用唔到呢支野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605fba5da5ebedd273e33328f3db444fea9b6a5b","tid":216761,"uid":6815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:50:24.000Z","msg":"究竟點解成日生飛滋架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無話點預防<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98979dc301fb2fe5398884c96d65640dd87f259","tid":216761,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟點解成日生飛滋架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無話點預防<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維他命B幫到你"},{"pid":"4ff232b6285cb957d4d4deb8faddeb02bcff34c9","tid":216761,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Update 返<br />\n<br />\n塊白色保護膜甩咗啦<br />\n<br />\n而家傷口好敏感，但唔痛<br />\n<br />\n諗緊好唔好搽多次</blockquote><br />\n唔好<br />\n佢唔痛就得啦<br />\n<br />\n支野好大殺傷力<br />\n搽落啲冇事嘅地方仲慘過生飛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd4cd25c6809690add85bb1837bcf2860c93bdb","tid":216761,"uid":95742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"我之前都成日生 試過一次生七粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痛到仆街<br />\n但係半年前開始用漱口水就好好多 咁耐淨係生過一兩粒<br />\n巴打可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a2a4708df7028386b1653590d87b4ddf8b7735","tid":216761,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a430d67feb4269980719ee06fc05c29d71fbad2","tid":216761,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:06:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟點解成日生飛滋架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無話點預防<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細菌 傷口 <br />\n熱氣係指唇 口腔腫脹 容易割傷<br />\n箍牙都易生"},{"pid":"e0416617ff8cd6f65294376ff15ca77338478dc5","tid":216761,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:07:54.000Z","msg":"之前試過連續2日食4粒奇異果 就自己好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf864ca2c2839c213ced84ead9c719b6345c5bad","tid":216761,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/25/201243_062fc9c7111b20c30be8a355a4fd6916.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F201243_062fc9c7111b20c30be8a355a4fd6916.jpg&h=184e8900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該咁多位巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用完，我覺得超恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恐怖在於痛楚定成效？</blockquote><br />\n上次用完好左一日, 第二日又粒飛滋又起返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係粒飛滋太勁定點"},{"pid":"99aa5442e16b89f22ef7b454ae26b32c292ddc79","tid":216761,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用必妥碘，好得，浪2日口已經好得7788<br />\n果陣個口有2粒飛滋查藥膏都唔好</blockquote><br />\n冇用 搞到成條利都黃色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲牙仲要勁乾 一磨卑晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a05c1286e46513ea090b9f8c9bf26887d4d1df","tid":216761,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>究竟點解成日生飛滋架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無話點預防<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維他命B幫到你</blockquote><br />\n少食花生 花生好似有種酵素會破壞口腔黏膜<br />\n我以前成日生  1個月生起碼一次<br />\n但自從飲多咗水後就冇乜點生過"},{"pid":"9d59a6b1faa12fc9bd9a67900ceb5020191b4287","tid":216761,"uid":58975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"我生左粒唔痛既飛滋，好唔番，好怕有事"},{"pid":"591512952987d4dfd3bf0a84b63c4e74b540f226","tid":216761,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前都成日生 試過一次生七粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痛到仆街<br />\n但係半年前開始用漱口水就好好多 咁耐淨係生過一兩粒<br />\n巴打可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢D係咪手足口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6ca0aa3a8554cb97a6cf40d1eaa26d6195ce87","tid":216761,"uid":2461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:44:00.000Z","msg":"第一次用口健樂勁有效<br />\n但第二次用 粒飛滋依然喺度不突止 重發炎搞到要睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f32a4cdcf8751c159f701326288fa572083e410","tid":216761,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"西瓜霜萬試萬靈"},{"pid":"f36a35c621712ca109df41c6a99cf95e2a7093e3","tid":216761,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:18:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西瓜霜萬試萬靈</blockquote><br />\n呢個我唔啱"},{"pid":"6d8d839b93d96a142c3f32e514fa6d5d2745d3e1","tid":216761,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"